description: The Roadie II Executive Backpack has the same professionally built quality as the rest of the popular Roadie collection, but in a size and configuration designed around traveling for business with a mobile office. There are three cascading storage sections that expand to fit a laptop, tablet, documents, gadgets, accessories and personal items. When the bag is zipped closed, these sections nest together for a slim profile that is carry-on and under-seat compatible for airlines, and looks the part around the office and in the conference room.
title: Tenba 638-337 Roadie II Executive Backpack
